From fb5dddd5362641f52b1e7992060b8690e57219eb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: medusa build <build@medusa.local>
Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2026 23:18:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(wallet): encrypted storage + account list --json +
 keycard disable (rc5 port)

Ports medusa rc4 0001/0002 onto rc5 (Argon2id+AES-256-GCM encrypted storage, mnemonic/key export, account list --json) and disables the keycard subcommand (upstream keycard shells out to a Python keycard_wallet module that isn't bundled and panics; now bails cleanly).
